Class DataCollect

java.lang.Object
  melting.DataCollect

public class DataCollect
extends java.lang.Object

This class is useful to extract the different thermodynamic parameters from the HashMap which contains them.

getSymetricSequencePairs

private java.lang.String getSymetricSequencePairs(java.lang.String seq1,
                                                  java.lang.String seq2)
builds the symmetric duplex (5'3' orientation) from the String seq1 and seq2

Parameters:
seq1 - : a sequence (5'3')
seq2 - : a complementary sequence (3'5')
Returns:
String symmetric duplex (5'3' orientation). Ex : seq1 = "AC" (5'3') seq2 = "TG" (3'5') symmetric duplex => "GT/CA" (5'3' orientation) with 5'"GT"3' and 3'"CA"5'
